School Passport Engagement
By Global Grid for Learning (GG4L)

This is the official School Passport extension that is part of school or district wide deployment to all student accounts.

The School Passport Engagement extension allows students to instantly launch their school admin provisioned applications and powers the Engagement Analytics Dashboard.

Learn more - gg4l.com
Contact - Info@gg4l.com
Privacy policy - gg4l.com/privacy-policy

School Passport and GG4L are an approved signatory of the Student Data Privacy Pledge, a recipient of the IMS TrustEd Apps Seal and a member of the Student Data Privacy Consortium.
